    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "伊莉雅开始怀疑自己的选择是否正确，\\n此时莫尔提斯给了她莫大的安慰。\\n一行人刚逃离一片火海的森林，\\n愤怒得失去理智的龙又向他们袭来。\\n千钧一发之际，碧龙挺身救场。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "总之先跑出这片森林！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（为了不让我们藏身，\\n竟然在森林里放火。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（奥古斯这男人\\n真是个彻头彻尾的混蛋……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（森林被烧又会引发魔力紊乱，\\n恐怕会惹恼龙吧。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（我想要做的事\\n真的是对的吗？\\n到底什么才是对的……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，你还能跑吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "梅奈、塞西娅，你们先走。\\n我来背伊莉雅，\\n等下就会追上你们的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "好，交给你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，走吧。\\n到我背上来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "抱歉……莫尔提斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "真的很抱歉……\\n把你召唤到了这样的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你原本是非常纯粹美丽的存在，\\n却沾染了污秽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅？你在说什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "毕竟这是事实吧？\\n被召唤出来、得到肉身之后，\\n你总是遇到这种倒霉事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我并不是出于这种目的\\n才把你召唤到这个世上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我本想教会你更多\\n关于世界、情感之类的\\n美丽的事物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但是……我无力阻止任何事。\\n反而还让事态恶化。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "什么才是对的，应该如何抉择\\n才能通往期盼的未来……\\n我一无所知。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "无知令人恐惧。\\n但是，还有更让我害怕的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那就是我也许无法保护你……\\n这让我非常害怕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以……你还是恢复自由的好。\\n我们就在这里分别吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你走吧。别让我成为你的负担，\\n去你想去的地方……\\n对你而言，这一定就是正确答案！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我们走，伊莉雅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你明白我在说什么吗？\\n你应该自由地……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我想去的地方就是有你的地方。\\n不跟你一起就没有意义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我们一直在一起。\\n这就是我的爱。\\n怎么样，这是正确答案吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "爱的正确答案因人而异，\\n这么说的好像是我呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这就是你的正确答案吗……\\n之后再后悔我可不管啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我有信心不会后悔。\\n好了，我们赶紧离开森林吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好！谢谢你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "他们两个，\\n还没从森林里出来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "到底是怎么了。\\n难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "我……要去帮他们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不行！太乱来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "乱来也得去啊！\\n伊莉雅她……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "让你们久等了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你们两个都没事啊。\\n太好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "抱歉，害你们担心了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "太好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我帮你疗伤，\\n让我看看你的脚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "大家都没事倒是好……\\n可王都的炸弹还没拆除，\\n怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "森林也被烧了。\\n这下又会惹恼龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "到头来我只是让情况恶化了。\\n接下来该怎么办……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "什么声音？\\n冲我们这边来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "这难道是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "大家快趴下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "龙！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是打算去王都吗。\\n得阻止他们才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "但是，这么多……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "龙",
            "context": "人类，不可原谅！\\n杀掉，杀掉人类！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "等等，我们并不想\\n和你们争斗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "龙",
            "context": "那么，为什么，\\n要烧掉原野、森林？\\n为什么屠杀，我们的同胞？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "龙",
            "context": "龙，被杀了。\\n杀掉，杀掉，杀掉人类……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "龙",
            "context": "杀杀杀杀杀杀杀！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "他们已经因为愤怒\\n而失去了理智。\\n我们只能逃了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "想逃也没路啊。\\n走投无路了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "龙，保护了我们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "耶梦加得！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶，耶梦加得！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（和迷雾森林的碧龙同名！？\\n而且这魔力，和碧龙如出一辙……\\n这头龙到底是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "都冷静点！就算杀掉人类，\\n同胞们也回不来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "就算是耶梦加得，\\n要对付这么多龙也……\\n我们也来帮忙吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "但要跟龙抗衡，\\n力量差距明摆着呢！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是啊，四个人合力，逐个击破。\\n只能不断这样做\\n直到全部打倒为止了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "哪怕只放过去一头，\\n王都都会发生爆炸……\\n只能这么办了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "看来是这样呢。\\n只能下定决心迎战了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我们齐心协力，\\n压制住愤怒的龙吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_06_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}